Bing is the king. by far

743
01:06:29.570 --> 01:06:33.407
Mutt has got Jeff
And Eleanor. FDR

744
01:06:39.872 --> 01:06:41.415
- We got Annie
- We got Annie

745
01:06:41.582 --> 01:06:43.042
We got Annie

746
01:06:54.136 --> 01:06:56.138
We got Annie

747
01:07:13.698 --> 01:07:15.825
We got Annie

748
01:07:46.063 --> 01:07:47.773
Annie

749
01:07:48.149 --> 01:07:52.403
It's a hard-knock life for us.

750
01:07:53.404 --> 01:07:58.159
It's a hard-knock life for us.

751
01:07:58.409 --> 01:08:03.038
No one cares for you a smidge...

752
01:08:03.289 --> 01:08:06.625
...when you're in an orphanage.

753
01:08:08.127 --> 01:08:11.881
What are you doing?

754
01:08:15.718 --> 01:08:20.222
Why aren't you marching in line
with the rest of them?

755
01:08:21.724 --> 01:08:26.812
Duffy. come here. Come on.

756
01:08:29.231 --> 01:08:35.488
You're hiding something
from Miss Hannigan behind your back.

757
01:08:35.654 --> 01:08:40.034
- No.
- Let me have it.

758
01:08:45.122 --> 01:08:47.333
Get inside!

759
01:08:52.838 --> 01:08:56.509
I've seen his picture in the paper
with President Roosevelt.

760
01:09:09.438 --> 01:09:12.650
- Hannigan. I presume?
- Yes.

761
01:09:12.858 --> 01:09:15.486
I want to talk to you about Annie.

762
01:09:16.487 --> 01:09:19.865
You want to return her and forget it.
or trade up?

763
01:09:20.366 --> 01:09:22.368
I want to adopt her.

764
01:09:23.035 --> 01:09:25.496
Would you excuse me for a moment?

765
01:09:34.547 --> 01:09:37.591
- Would you care to step into my office?
- Thank you.

766
01:09:44.014 --> 01:09:46.559
Hi. sweetie.

