Ten years ago. we left our
little baby girl on the front steps.

1040
01:30:30.468 --> 01:30:36.140
There was a job managing a hotel.
but only if we had no children.

1041
01:30:36.349 --> 01:30:41.229
- Wrap it up.
- We never meant to leave Annie.

1042
01:30:42.939 --> 01:30:46.776
Now we have a hardware store in
New Jersey. We can take care of her.

1043
01:30:47.026 --> 01:30:48.528
We've always loved her.

1044
01:30:49.862 --> 01:30:54.826
- You're Annie's parents?
- We live over the store.

1045
01:30:55.618 --> 01:30:58.496
- There's a yard out back.
- With chickens.

1046
01:30:58.746 --> 01:31:00.748
And a rooster.

1047
01:31:05.503 --> 01:31:07.004
Rooster?

1048
01:31:10.716 --> 01:31:15.346
My God! I never would
have recognized you.

1049
01:31:19.934 --> 01:31:23.688
If we can fool you.
we can fool "Big Bucks."

1050
01:31:23.980 --> 01:31:27.859
- Fifty thousand smackers.
- You'll be the death of me.

1051
01:31:28.067 --> 01:31:32.697
Sis. this is going to be
the best bunco job ever.

1052
