- We need details.
- About Annie. Specifics.

1053
01:31:38.703 --> 01:31:43.416
- What's in it for me'?
- A three-way split of the $50.000.

1054
01:31:43.666 --> 01:31:46.210
- I want half.
- All right. half!

1055
01:31:46.377 --> 01:31:48.713
- Rooster!
- All right!

1056
01:31:48.880 --> 01:31:53.718
Twenty-five grand for me and Lil.
25 grand for you.

1057
01:31:56.512 --> 01:31:59.765
Why don't we wait
and see what she's got.

1058
01:32:00.433 --> 01:32:03.936
See if it's worth 25 grand.

1059
01:32:04.187 --> 01:32:07.398
You want details? I've got details.

1060
01:32:07.565 --> 01:32:10.193
I've got specifics on every kid
in this dump.

1061
01:32:10.359 --> 01:32:13.196
It's just finding the right box.

1062
01:32:15.448 --> 01:32:19.577
Annie wears a locket around her neck.

1063
01:32:20.453 --> 01:32:22.496
It's a broken locket.

1064
01:32:22.705 --> 01:32:27.710
She says her parents saved the other
half to come and claim her with.

1065
01:32:28.169 --> 01:32:33.007
Years ago.
her parents were killed in a fire.

1066
01:32:33.633 --> 01:32:35.718
The cops brought me all their junk.

1067
01:32:35.927 --> 01:32:38.137
Well. my darling baby brother...

1068
01:32:38.304 --> 01:32:42.975
...if Annie's parents can claim her
with that locket. so can we.

1069
01:32:43.768 --> 01:32:48.189
- Fifty thousand smackers.
- The kid we'll drop in the river.

1070
01:32:48.439 --> 01:32:52.026
They're going to do
something bad to Annie!

1071
01:32:52.235 --> 01:32:55.238
- Have you cleaned the can?
- Listen to me. I mean it.

1072
01:32:55.446 --> 01:32:56.822
Clean the can!

1073
01:32:57.031 --> 01:33:01.535
- Duffy. Tessie. somebody!
- Do you want a knuckle sandwich?

1074
01:33:01.786 --> 01:33:04.205
- We've got to warn Annie!
- Scrub!

1075
01:33:04.830 --> 01:33:07.875
It's in a sealed envelope.

1076
01:33:08.042 --> 01:33:11.587
It ain't fair how we scrounge
For three or four bucks

1077
01:33:11.754 --> 01:33:13.089
While she gets Warbucks

1078
01:33:13.256 --> 01:33:15.508
The little brat. Look in those!

1079
01:33:15.675 --> 01:33:18.636
It ain't fair
This here life is driving me nuts

1080
01:33:18.803 --> 01:33:20.054
Make yourself useful!

1081
01:33:20.221 --> 01:33:22.139
When we get peanuts

1082
01:33:22.974 --> 01:33:24.392
She's living fat

1083
01:33:24.809 --> 01:33:26.644
Maybe she holds the key

1084
01:33:26.811 --> 01:33:29.438
- That little lady
- To getting more bucks

1085
01:33:29.605 --> 01:33:32.483
- Right. instead of less.
- It'll have her name on it.

1086
01:33:32.650 --> 01:33:37.655
Maybe we fix it again
With something shady

1087
01:33:37.822 --> 01:33:40.866
Where does that put us?

1088
01:33:44.578 --> 01:33:46.497
Give you one guess

1089
01:33:50.835 --> 01:33:51.961
Open it.

1090
01:33:55.298 --> 01:33:57.550
Hurry.

1091
01:34:00.094 --> 01:34:02.138
Easy Street

1092
01:34:04.515 --> 01:34:07.935
Easy Street

1093
01:34:08.227 --> 01:34:14.817
- Annie is the key
- Yes. sirree

1094
01:34:16.986 --> 01:34:20.239
<i>- Easy Street
- We'll live the plush life</i>

1095
01:34:20.406 --> 01:34:23.784
- Easy Street
- The lazy. lush life

1096
01:34:23.951 --> 01:34:27.330
Better get there

1097
01:34:29.874 --> 01:34:31.917
The gravy's flowing there

1098
01:34:33.836 --> 01:34:35.963
We'll soon be going there

1099
01:34:36.130 --> 01:34:40.259
Where you sleep till noon

1100
01:34:40.426 --> 01:34:42.303
Yeah. yeah. yeah

1101
01:34:44.513 --> 01:34:48.517
- Move them feet
- Move them ever-loving feet

1102
01:34:48.684 --> 01:34:52.063
- To Easy Street
- Where living's sweet

1103
01:34:52.229 --> 01:34:56.067
That's where we're gonna be

1104
01:34:57.610 --> 01:35:00.571
Easy Street

1105
01:35:01.655 --> 01:35:04.408
Easy Street

1106
01:36:15.646 --> 01:36:20.192
Move them feet to Easy Street

1107
01:36:21.235 --> 01:36:31.829
That's where we're gonna

1108
01:36:44.800 --> 01:36:46.469
Hit it. sis.

1109
01:36:56.395 --> 01:37:01.442
That's where we're gonna

1110
01:37:01.609 --> 01:37:03.819
Stay

1111
01:37:08.699 --> 01:37:13.204
Easy Street

1112
01:37:22.963 --> 01:37:25.341
Now do the other one.

1113
01:37:34.600 --> 01:37:38.479
Duffy. Tessie. somebody! They're
going to do something to Annie!

1114
01:37:38.687 --> 01:37:40.397
- Who is?
- They are!

1115
01:37:40.648 --> 01:37:42.441
- Who's they?
- Miss Hannigan.

1116
01:37:42.691 --> 01:37:44.318
Oh. my goodness!

1117
01:37:48.822 --> 01:37:50.783
Beautiful.

1118
01:37:57.456 --> 01:38:01.627
