Get in that closet.

1121
01:38:16.559 --> 01:38:18.727
Stop it!

1122
01:38:23.816 --> 01:38:27.069
Whose rotten idea was this?

1123
01:39:02.187 --> 01:39:04.189
Are they here?

1124
01:39:04.440 --> 01:39:08.402
A man who counts his chickens before
they hatch gets a scrambled egg.

1125
01:39:08.569 --> 01:39:10.195
What?

1126
01:39:14.033 --> 01:39:19.330
- Have my parents come for me?
- We haven't found them.

1127
