I interviewed 865 couples.
None of them knew about the locket.

1128
01:39:51.904 --> 01:39:55.908
I never realized how many dishonest
people there are in New York.

1129
01:40:17.388 --> 01:40:23.060
They're dead. I guess I've known
that deep down for a long time.

1130
01:40:23.227 --> 01:40:26.355
I'm not giving up. so don't you.

1131
01:40:26.522 --> 01:40:31.151
I didn't want to be just another
orphan. I wanted to be special.

1132
01:40:31.402 --> 01:40:35.948
You are special.
Never stop believing that.

1133
01:40:36.782 --> 01:40:39.076
We're trapped.

1134
01:40:44.289 --> 01:40:47.626
Oh. my goodness. Oh. my goodness.

1135
01:40:48.961 --> 01:40:52.423
- We'll never get out of here.
- I've got an idea.

1136
01:40:54.258 --> 01:40:57.845
Great idea.

1137
