Quiet down. girls.

1223
01:50:35.463 --> 01:50:39.676
You want to see Mr. Warbucks?
All right. come on.

1224
01:51:10.915 --> 01:51:13.043
Oh. my goodness!

1225
01:51:36.358 --> 01:51:39.361
- What now?
- Sir.

1226
01:51:39.611 --> 01:51:42.572
- I think he's a highness.
- Your Highness.

1227
01:51:42.822 --> 01:51:46.201
