- Leaping lizards!

1230
01:52:00.048 --> 01:52:02.675
You take the autocopter.
I'll take the car.

1231
01:52:02.884 --> 01:52:07.889
J. Edgar? Warbucks here.
Orphan Annie has been kidnapped.

1232
01:52:08.098 --> 01:52:11.976
I want every G-man on this
in the next 20 minutes.

1233
01:52:14.729 --> 01:52:17.065
Where's the fire. fellas?

1234
01:53:23.214 --> 01:53:26.676
The truck is on Canal Street.
heading east.

1235
01:53:27.051 --> 01:53:31.264
East on Canal.
Well done. Punjab. Don't lose them.

1236
01:53:34.350 --> 01:53:39.439
Can we stop? I've got to go.

1237
01:53:41.566 --> 01:53:44.027
I've really got to. Miss Hannigan.

1238
01:53:45.904 --> 01:53:50.783
I mean it. When you've got to go.
you've got to go.

1239
01:53:59.501 --> 01:54:01.544
Make it fast.

1240
01:54:05.256 --> 01:54:08.218
Rooster. grab her!
She's got the check!

1241
01:54:12.680 --> 01:54:16.809
- Cut her off at the bridge.
- Goddamn it!

1242
01:54:17.685 --> 01:54:20.104
Come back here. you goddamn kid!

1243
01:54:42.710 --> 01:54:45.129
Mr. Warbucks will eat your livers.

1244
01:54:45.338 --> 01:54:50.468
- I'll kill you.
- He's really going to kill her.

1245
01:54:51.886 --> 01:54:56.975
Rooster! Rooster. stop!

1246
01:54:58.268 --> 01:55:01.145
Rooster. she's a baby.

1247
01:55:03.189 --> 01:55:05.024
Come back here.

1248
01:55:10.572 --> 01:55:11.614
Rooster!

1249
01:55:11.781 --> 01:55:15.118
- I'm gonna kill her!
